title: Bloomberg Markets: Collins on Active Set to Strike Back

description:
Bloomberg Markets with Carol Massar and Cory Johnson. GUEST: Margaret Collins Investing Team Leader Bloomberg Editorial Discussing her chats with active managers, including David Hunt Prudential Financial, who say active investing will strike back.
